Ntarindwa Diogene ni umunya[[rwanda]] wavukiye i [[Burundi]] muri 1977<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=5587</ref>, wamenyekanye nka '''Atome''' cyane mu gukina byendagusetsa, ni Umwanditsi  n'umukinnyi wa filimi, ikinamico na comedy<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/80765</ref><ref>http://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/yabimburiye-abato-mu-nzira-y-inzitane-ibaruwa-ya-ntarindwa-diogene-atome-kuri</ref>. yamenyekanye mu ikinamico nka '''Gasumuni,''' yatangiye gukina ikinamico muri 1994<ref>https://www.jeuneafrique.com/202488/culture/diog-ne-ntarindwa/</ref><ref>https://www.theatre-contemporain.net/biographies/Diogene-Ntarindwa</ref>.

== Atome mu gusetsa ==
Atome  gukina amakinamico yabikoze cyane yiga muri kaminuza y'u [[Rwanda]] mu iishami ry'amategeko muri 1996<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/86347/ntarindwa-diogene-uzwi-nka-atome-yagiye-mu-butaliyani-aho-agiye-gukinira-umukino-bise-hate-86347.html</ref>. muri 2002 yagiye gukomeza amasomo i Liege  mu [[Ububiligi]] ibijyanye na Art Dramatique naho akomeza gukina aho yagaragaye mu ma kinamico arimo Koulsy Lamko, Corpx et voix, Paroles rhizome<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/imyidagaduro/sinema/article/umubyeyi-wa-gasumuni-azashyingurwa-ku-wa-gatandatu</ref><ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/57688/byinshi-utari-uzi-kuri-ntarindwa-diogene-wamenyekanye-mu-gusetsa-ku-izina-rya-atome-gasumuni--57688.html</ref>. muri 2008 yagarutse mu [[Rwanda]] agaragara cyane akina asetsa muri forum yari yateguwe n'Imbuto Foundation Rwanda<ref>https://mediatheques-ifbf.org/index.php?lvl=author_see&id=19885</ref><ref>https://www.bunker.si/en/events/diogene-ntarindwa-atome-interview-conversation/</ref>.

== Atome mu gisirikare ==
'''Atome''' mu rugamba rwo kubohora igihugu 1994 yarimo nk'umusirikare, avuga ko yakigiyem akiri umujene niyompamvu urugamba rurangiye yagiye gukomeza amashuri.<ref>https://www.ulk.ac.rw/news/monsieur-madame-theatre-troupe-performs-ulk-kigali/</ref><ref>https://www.crew-united.com/en/Diogene-Ntarindwa_482716.html</ref>

